me.desht.sensibletoolbox.api.recipes

Class FuelItems

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.desht.sensibletoolbox.api.recipes.FuelItems

  • public class FuelItems
extends Object
    Represents items that may be converted to SCU by some machine. A machine which does this conversion can create a static instance of this object, to effectively use as a fuel dictionary.
